HEADWORD: flannelcake
<hw>flannelcake</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a flat cake of thin batter fried
on both sides on a griddle; a pancake; a flapjack.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> pancake, battercake, flapcake, flapjack,
griddlecake, hotcake, hot cake.</syn>⟦br⟧
